{
  "id": "adv_event_2604_02_06",
  "title": "もぐもぐ！ブリスケ！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ただいま～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 3.2660318375,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2666.6666667000004
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_05-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "お帰りなさい～！　ご飯出来てるわよ\n今夜のメインディッシュはなんと私が釣り上げた大物よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.4666666667,
      "endTime": 13.391768709800001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_05-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ～！　楽しみだな～！\nお腹ペコペコだよ～！　夕飯はなんだろう～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.6,
      "endTime": 22.9043306351,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_05-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "ご飯とみそ汁とお漬物と私が釣ったブ……\nあら？　千紗ちゃん、どこ行くの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.1,
      "endTime": 32.6335605622,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_05-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "ご飯の前に服、着替えて来るね\nちょっと濡れてるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.8333333333,
      "endTime": 38.260839112599996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_05-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "……ねえ、怜ちゃん。みんな元気ないみたいだけど\nどうしたの？　何かあった？　夕飯食べれそう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.4666666667,
      "endTime": 49.1666662852,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 22266.666666600002
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_05-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、大丈夫よ。命の大切さについて学んで来たの\n全ての食べ物に、感謝をしないと。私も着替えて来るわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.3666666667,
      "endTime": 62.3474681322,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_05-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "（あら、雫ちゃんは着替える前に食べてるわね）\n（よっぽどお腹が空いていたのかしら……？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.0333328247,
      "endTime": 71.71213130950001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_05-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん……今日のブリカマ……\nいつもよりちょっぴりしょっぱいや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.8999994914,
      "endTime": 80.9999996821,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}